user_name: NHS North Central London CCG – Haringey
user_description: Working to improve health and care for Haringey as part of north central London clinical commissioning group (@NHS_NCLCCG). Monitored Mon - Fri, 9am - 5pm.
text:
You can get your #CovidVaccine at Bounds Green Group Practice’s walk-in Pfizer vaccination clinic. Open today between 9am - 1pm.

No booking needed. Everyone aged 16+ can get a jab. Second doses given 8 weeks after the 1st. https://t.co/oQhOrn4mMO

user_description: NHS Merton is part of the NHS South West London CCG and is responsible for planning and delivering most of the healthcare services for Merton residents.
text: If you’re 18 plus come and get your Pfizer #COVIDVaccine from the friendly Hilton Pharmacy Team at Morden Assembly Hall today. We’re open from 9am to 1pm. If the weather is hot, don't forget to keep well hydrated before your jab! Find all our walk-ins here https://t.co/fUPDqbqrFd https://t.co/RVTXzuWX36
